0002.Tooltip:
Zeratul is the prominent elite within dark templars. He can harness powerful void psi, granting him more health and attack. Mysterious dark templar Zeratul is persistently searching for the legacy left by Xel'naga. When he is exquisitely harness the power of void, he also acquire the reverence from Koprulu sector through his wisdom. He can use Shadow Strike, Void Prison, Blink, Void Armor, and Whispers of Oblivion. He is permanently cloaked. Zeratul require 60 seconds to warp into the battle field.

Can attack the ground and air.
0002.Name: Warp In Zeratul

0002.Tooltip: Conclave Pheonix. This air-specialized fighter has very fast movement speed and can automatically fire Neutron Bomb to attack target unit. Angel Wings can emit beams to attack air unit, lifting ground unit to the air and attacking them.
0002.Name: Warp Angel Wings

0002.Tooltip: Conclave Void Rays. This continuous strike vessel can attack three units simultaneously, and will increase its damage and attack range during the process. Holy Light Prism can easily deal with heavy armor unit. Also, enemy attacked by them will be exposed and receive more damage.
0002.Name: Warp Holy Light Prism

0002.Tooltip: Basic worker unit. Can gather resources and warp in Protoss structures.**Can attack ground units**
0002.Name: Warp In Probe

0002.Name: Warp In Tempest

Detector
0002.Name: Warp In Oracle

0002.Tooltip:
A moving casting unit. Capable to use Phase Cannon, Mass Recall, Time Warp. Can be upgraded to Shield of Aiur.

Can attack ground and air units.
0002.Name: Warp In Mothership Core

0002.Tooltip: A long-range infantry mech with extra health and attack power. Applying for the Ara Tribe protocol allows Dragoon to attack extra targets and increase damage to air units.**Can attack the ground and air**
0002.Name: Warp In Dragoon

0003.Name: Warp In Colossus

0003.Name: Warp in Instigator

0003.Tooltip: Area Siege Unit. Can produce and shoot Scarabs, dealing bursting damage. After applying for the Finax Tribe Protocol, it can produce and shoot Scarabs faster and deal higher aoe damage after research. **Can attack ground**
0003.Name: Warp In Reaver
